OL,3,CLeeds mum spent over a decade learning
OL,4,Cto walk again after being hit by a car
OL,6,FA Leeds mum who spent 14 years
OL,7,Flearning to walk again after being hit
OL,8,Fby a car is raising awareness of the
OL,9,Frealities of living with major trauma.
OL,11,FAmy Stevenson, 40, was left brain
OL,12,Fdamaged and paralysed at eight years
OL,13,Fold after being hit by a car as she
OL,14,Fwalked near her home in Cookridge,
OL,15,FLeeds.
OL,17,FShe was waiting to cross a busy road
OL,18,Fwith her friend when a car came past,
OL,19,Fdriving too fast and too close to the
OL,20,Fcurb. She was knocked unconscious and
OL,21,Ftaken to hospital.
