OL,3,CLeeds mum spent over a decade learning
OL,4,Cto walk again after being hit by a car
OL,6,FMrs Stevenson said: "I spent two weeks
OL,7,Fin intensive care and was in hospital
OL,8,Ffor another six weeks."
OL,10,FThe accident left her with a serious
OL,11,Fbrain injury, broken left femur and
OL,12,Fparalysed down one side. She feared
OL,13,Fshe would never walk again.
OL,15,FMrs Stevenson said: "I had a dream and
OL,16,FI wanted my life to be a certain way
OL,17,Fand I was determined to make it happen
OL,18,Fif I could.
OL,20,F"So I wasn't going to give up unless
OL,21,Fsomeone told me you won't walk again."
