OL,3,CLeeds mum spent over a decade learning
OL,4,Cto walk again after being hit by a car
OL,6,FAfter undergoing 14 years of
OL,7,Fdetermined rehabilitation, countless
OL,8,Fsurgeries and visiting specialists in
OL,9,FAmerica, she walked for the first time
OL,10,Funaided in 2006 at 22-years-old.
OL,12,FThe mother of three now volunteers
OL,13,Fwith the charity Day One Trauma which
OL,14,Fsupports major trauma patients and
OL,15,Ftheir families in the UK.
OL,17,FAs part of the charity's Major Trauma
OL,18,FAwareness Week a new 'Dear Me'
OL,19,Fcampaign has been launched.
