OL,4,Cto walk again after being hit by a car
OL,6,FThe campaign encourages people
OL,7,Faffected by a catastrophic injury to
OL,8,Fwrite to their younger selves, with
OL,9,FMrs Stevenson's letter being shared on
OL,10,Fthe Day One Trauma Supports website.
OL,12,FMr Stevenson said: "I found it very
OL,13,Ftherapeutic for myself to look back at
OL,14,Fwhat I used to think about when I was
OL,15,Fa teenager.
OL,17,F"When I was reliant on a wheelchair
OL,18,Fand reliant on someone pushing me
OL,19,Faround all the time it was hard to see
OL,20,Fany future."
