OL,4,Cto walk again after being hit by a car
OL,6,FA spokesperson at Day One Trauma
OL,7,FSupport said: "Although Amy's and the
OL,8,Fother letters are unique, there's
OL,9,Fconstant themes of loneliness,
OL,10,Fisolation and having to get through
OL,11,Ftimes on their own."
OL,13,FThe charity hopes to use the recurring
OL,14,Fthemes brought up in the letters to
OL,15,Finform the support given to others in
OL,16,Fthe future.
OL,18,FDiscussing how far she has come Mrs
OL,19,FStevenson said she is living a life
OL,20,Fshe "didn't think possible".
